=> projects/ozpex-micro.gmi Ozpex Micro - An 8-bit computer architecture designed for extensibility
=> projects/os-micro.gmi OS/Micro - A full operating system stack and programming language for the Ozpex Micro
=> projects/quadraserve.gmi Quadraserve - A 4-protocol web server that supports CGI-like scripts
